&D              rt ra si
@D              ...... rt:5 ra:5 si:s16                 &D

%ds_si          2:s14  !function=times_4
@DS             ...... rt:5 ra:5 .............. ..      &D si=%ds_si

&X              rt ra rb
@X              ...... rt:5 ra:5 rb:5 .......... .      &X

